568
00:40:03,520 --> 00:40:06,180
would be a waste for us.

569
00:40:06,180 --> 00:40:09,340
So this is one of the main
confusions that happens.

570
00:40:09,340 --> 00:40:12,460
If you can keep
yourself straight,

571
00:40:12,460 --> 00:40:15,310
you're a lot better
off, and as I

