00:45:06,310 --> 00:45:08,110
And I just don't
wanna have to keep

640
00:45:08,110 --> 00:45:10,250
on writing all those symbols.

641
00:45:10,250 --> 00:45:13,850
It's a waste of
blackboard energy.

642
00:45:13,850 --> 00:45:15,500
There's a total
