668
00:46:48,230 --> 00:46:54,330
There's a total of n possible
times that that happens.

669
00:46:54,330 --> 00:46:59,110
And now the great thing
is that, with this alone,

670
00:46:59,110 --> 00:47:05,120
all the rest of the
